<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-12954] system_distributed.view_build_status uses gc_gs of 0, but issues distributed deletes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-12954</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The definition uses &lt;tt&gt;CFMetaData.compile()&lt;/tt&gt; method, intended for non-replicated system-keyspace tables, and doesn&apos;t override gc_grace_seconds from 0, but does issue deletes. This can lead to entries in the table not being cleaned up.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13023225">CASSANDRA-12954</key>
