                            <comment id="15719328" author="jjirsa" created="Sun, 4 Dec 2016 04:58:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Adding to all tables in &lt;tt&gt;system_distributed&lt;/tt&gt; - we may not automatically deleted from repair_history or parent_repair_history, but they&apos;re replicated, so if a user issues deletes, it should get a proper gcgs to be safe.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CI pending, should be ready tomorrow:&lt;/p&gt;

